# Flask + MySQL CRUD App

A simple web application built with **Flask** and **MySQL** that demonstrates CRUD (Create, Read, Update, Delete) operations.  
This project manages customer records with a clean UI and backend integration.

---

## 🚀 Features
- Add new customers
- View customer list
- Update customer details
- Delete customers
- MySQL database integration

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack
- **Backend:** Python (Flask)
- **Database:** MySQL
- **Frontend:** HTML, CSS (Jinja2 templates)
- **Deployment Ready:** Requirements file included

